D3R-positive and D3R-negative terminals in the mNAcSh and total NAc area. 
Note the lack of expression in the Islands of Calleja (ICj) in mice expressing 
Cre-OFF ChR2 in the ventral striatum. b, oIPSCs originating from D3R-positive 
and D3R-negative collaterals were recorded from mNAcSh D1-MSNs or D2-MSNs. 
c,g,k,o, Time-course of oIPSCs in mNAcSh MSNs (c; two-way repeated-measures 
ANOVA: time effect, F(3.099,89.38) = 39.75, P < 0.0001; treatment effect, F(1,29) = 28.21, 
